                        Concedo. et Confirmo per hoc principale scriptum in perpetuum. <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">Monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3000">Sancti
                            Laurentii</orgName> levite et martiris christi. sito circa <rs
                            key="#Walls">muros</rs> nostrae <placeName key="#Cities #Walls"
